# downloaded

**Type Property**

A local copy of this item exists, but it is stale. The most recent version will be downloaded as soon as possible.

## Declaration

```swift
static let downloaded: URLUbiquitousItemDownloadingStatus
```

## Constants

- **current**: A local copy of this item exists and is the most up-to-date version known to the device.
- **notDownloaded**: This item has not been downloaded yet. Use [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/FileManager/startDownloadingUbiquitousItem(at:)] to download it.
